edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.examples
Class FrameWriteSummary

java.lang.Object
  edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.examples.FrameWriteSummary

public class FrameWriteSummary
extends java.lang.Object

This example will search the bitstream for FDRI write commands and will summarize the FAR locations for each FDRI command. It supports bitstreams with multiple FDRI commands.
